lastfm-python-mirbuild (0.2.14) stable; urgency=low

  * improvements to packaging of Python projects:
    - switch from dh_pysupport (deprecated) to dh_python2
    - allow more customisation of autogenerated setup.py files
  * improvements to Debian packaging:
    - make targets in debian/rules files more easily customisable
    - allow passing options to call to 'dh'
    - new prepare_package method in Project class which can be
      overridden by subclasses
  * removed obsolete fspath module from mirbuild
  * added python-pytest to dependencies (of both source and binary packages)
  * minor fixes and clean-ups

